WEBVTT

00:01:00.945 --> 00:01:02.465
Just admit you made a bad decision

00:01:02.545 --> 00:01:04.185
and ended up with a bad wife!

00:01:04.265 --> 00:01:06.705
I regret nothing more
than deciding to marry you.

00:01:06.785 --> 00:01:08.625
Are you sure about getting divorced?

00:01:08.705 --> 00:01:10.665
Yes. We've talked about it.

00:01:10.745 --> 00:01:13.185
No one's watching.
Why are you being nice to me?

00:01:14.265 --> 00:01:15.745
I just wanted to treat
an old lady to dinner

00:01:15.825 --> 00:01:17.865
so she wouldn't starve to death.

00:01:17.945 --> 00:01:18.865
Mom!

00:01:22.665 --> 00:01:23.825
Runch.

00:01:24.425 --> 00:01:26.905
Runch, wait. Runch.

00:01:26.985 --> 00:01:28.945
I really didn't mean it.

00:01:30.785 --> 00:01:31.905
Please go home.

00:01:32.945 --> 00:01:34.505
Are you mad at me?

00:01:38.145 --> 00:01:39.185
Runch.

00:01:42.665 --> 00:01:44.145
Runch…

00:01:48.465 --> 00:01:49.945
Peeracha!

00:02:00.705 --> 00:02:02.945
-Let me take care of your wound.
-Don't.

00:02:07.905 --> 00:02:09.265
I have to.

00:02:11.385 --> 00:02:13.745
Because my mom hurt you.

00:02:25.465 --> 00:02:28.585
Ow! Ow! That hurts!

00:02:31.225 --> 00:02:33.065
Please bear with me a little.

00:02:49.225 --> 00:02:50.825
I just need to clean up around it.

00:02:51.545 --> 00:02:53.905
-Ow!
-It doesn't hurt that bad, Neen.

00:02:53.985 --> 00:02:57.825
I'm just cleaning up around it.
I'm not touching your wound.

00:03:13.465 --> 00:03:16.465
Neen. This one's gonna sting a little.

00:03:58.105 --> 00:03:59.305
You're all set.

00:04:02.065 --> 00:04:04.505
I apologize on my mom's behalf.

00:04:12.385 --> 00:04:14.345
Let me walk you upstairs.

00:04:15.625 --> 00:04:16.705
Don't.

00:04:58.305 --> 00:05:00.345
You always act this way.

00:05:01.945 --> 00:05:04.505
This is why I could never get over you.

00:05:18.825 --> 00:05:21.105
Have you thought this through, Mrs. Warin?

00:05:21.185 --> 00:05:24.865
Suing for divorce means digging up
every part of your relationship.

00:05:26.145 --> 00:05:28.625
Some of them can hurt you
more than you'd expect.

00:05:30.465 --> 00:05:34.105
I've been hurt long enough.
I've been so hurt I've gone numb.

00:05:36.305 --> 00:05:40.225
My husband is the type
to give me false hopes.

00:05:41.265 --> 00:05:44.945
He only acts nice to me
in front of people.

00:05:46.385 --> 00:05:49.625
But when he gets home,
he's always with his parents.

00:05:50.465 --> 00:05:53.505
He acts as if I'm not there.

00:05:54.625 --> 00:05:56.585
I don't want to live
with this type of guy anymore.

00:06:01.425 --> 00:06:04.345
Let's start with your marital property,
shall we?

00:06:05.105 --> 00:06:08.625
Your house, car, savings, and stocks…

00:06:08.705 --> 00:06:10.785
everything you've had
since you got married.

00:06:10.865 --> 00:06:12.665
Do you have any records showing

00:06:12.745 --> 00:06:14.345
they were acquired or paid for jointly?

00:06:14.425 --> 00:06:17.065
I do. But it was all me.

00:06:17.585 --> 00:06:19.305
He never even made an effort.

00:06:22.545 --> 00:06:26.545
Any assets you've acquired
during your marriage

00:06:26.625 --> 00:06:29.265
count as marital property by law.

00:06:30.585 --> 00:06:33.585
They count as jointly-owned property.

00:06:34.465 --> 00:06:36.545
Any salary earned

00:06:36.625 --> 00:06:38.385
and any property acquired

00:06:38.465 --> 00:06:40.705
is considered marital property,

00:06:40.785 --> 00:06:42.785
even if it's in just one person's name.

00:06:44.865 --> 00:06:46.345
Anyway,

00:06:46.425 --> 00:06:48.625
I'll take care of every process for you.

00:06:49.505 --> 00:06:51.465
You're not alone in this.

00:06:53.185 --> 00:06:57.385
You know, sometimes
we don't really need much.

00:06:58.905 --> 00:07:01.705
It's enough just to feel loved

00:07:01.785 --> 00:07:03.505
and supported.

00:07:03.585 --> 00:07:06.505
Sometimes the one who loves the most

00:07:07.585 --> 00:07:09.985
is the one who's more tired than anyone.

00:07:10.065 --> 00:07:12.545
You seem to know the feeling well.

00:07:16.105 --> 00:07:19.065
It's my duty to understand
how my clients feel.

00:07:23.225 --> 00:07:25.785
Let's go, guys. It's Friday.

00:07:25.865 --> 00:07:28.945
We should party. Our usual place, okay?

00:07:29.625 --> 00:07:31.945
Sure! But is it your treat?

00:07:32.025 --> 00:07:34.385
Because if not, I'm not going.

00:07:34.465 --> 00:07:36.145
Come on, man.

00:07:39.225 --> 00:07:40.425
Boss,

00:07:41.585 --> 00:07:45.985
our department is having a party tonight.

00:07:46.065 --> 00:07:47.865
I was wondering

00:07:48.625 --> 00:07:50.145
if you'd want to treat us to dinner.

00:07:51.305 --> 00:07:53.585
So you all want to have a party?

00:07:54.505 --> 00:07:55.945
Yes, we do.

00:07:56.025 --> 00:07:59.225
Lately, we've been working very hard,

00:07:59.305 --> 00:08:01.105
so we wanted you to treat us to dinner

00:08:01.185 --> 00:08:03.345
to motivate us.

00:08:03.425 --> 00:08:05.065
Sure thing.

00:08:06.865 --> 00:08:09.265
Order as much as you like,

00:08:09.905 --> 00:08:11.425
but I'm going too.

00:08:13.225 --> 00:08:14.625
You're going too?

00:08:14.705 --> 00:08:16.425
Of course I am.

00:08:17.185 --> 00:08:20.185
I've never been to a party
with our department,

00:08:20.785 --> 00:08:23.505
so I want to find out
just how tired everyone is from work.

00:08:24.065 --> 00:08:26.185
I want a chance to talk to everyone

00:08:27.185 --> 00:08:30.425
as a team member, not just as the boss.

00:08:33.625 --> 00:08:35.545
-See you there.
-Sure.

00:08:40.945 --> 00:08:42.625
This won't be fun.

00:08:42.705 --> 00:08:46.185
Actually, this will be even more fun.

00:08:48.945 --> 00:08:49.785
Come on, everyone!

00:08:49.865 --> 00:08:51.665
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

00:09:00.745 --> 00:09:03.945
Boss, aren't you drinking?

00:09:05.545 --> 00:09:09.785
-Chug! Chug!
-Chug! Chug!

00:09:09.865 --> 00:09:12.425
-Chug! Chug!
-Chug! Chug!

00:09:18.545 --> 00:09:19.785
Come on, Boss.

00:09:20.745 --> 00:09:24.225
Does your wife only let you drink
soft, expensive wine?

00:09:24.825 --> 00:09:27.985
Judging from the way cheap booze
got you in that state.

00:09:29.505 --> 00:09:31.025
Come on, Utt.

00:09:31.105 --> 00:09:33.745
-Stop making her drink.
-Aw, come on.

00:09:35.425 --> 00:09:36.945
-Drink with me.
-Here.

00:09:37.025 --> 00:09:38.025
Boss.

00:09:38.105 --> 00:09:40.585
Do you want to call Ms. Peeracha
and tell her to pick you up?

00:09:41.505 --> 00:09:42.665
What?

00:09:43.905 --> 00:09:45.865
If I call her,

00:09:46.585 --> 00:09:48.305
she won't pick up.

00:09:51.545 --> 00:09:53.145
Please call her for me.

00:09:54.065 --> 00:09:56.545
I'll dial her number for you.

00:09:58.825 --> 00:10:00.225
It's…

00:10:02.665 --> 00:10:04.265
this number.

00:10:06.145 --> 00:10:08.025
I'll call her right away.

00:10:26.105 --> 00:10:27.465
Hello.

00:10:31.665 --> 00:10:33.105
Runch is really drunk?

00:10:34.545 --> 00:10:37.225
Got it. I'll pick her up right away.

00:10:38.145 --> 00:10:40.305
Okay. Thank you. Bye.

00:10:46.385 --> 00:10:48.505
She's drunk?!

00:10:56.185 --> 00:10:57.545
Boss.

00:10:57.625 --> 00:10:58.985
Boss!

00:10:59.905 --> 00:11:01.505
If you don't mind me asking,

00:11:01.585 --> 00:11:03.985
your fancy car,

00:11:04.065 --> 00:11:06.025
your ten million baht house,

00:11:06.105 --> 00:11:08.145
and your designer clothes…

00:11:08.785 --> 00:11:10.105
Did your wife buy them for you?

00:11:12.025 --> 00:11:13.545
Damn, Boss.

00:11:13.625 --> 00:11:16.305
You sure married into money!

00:11:17.505 --> 00:11:19.825
Quit saying that already.

00:11:20.825 --> 00:11:23.985
What, Boss?
Do you get aggressive when you drink?

00:11:24.905 --> 00:11:27.105
I was just teasing you.

00:11:27.745 --> 00:11:31.265
Everyone knows you're living off her.

00:11:39.305 --> 00:11:41.065
So you're jealous of me

00:11:42.345 --> 00:11:43.785
for having a rich,

00:11:44.505 --> 00:11:46.385
beautiful wife,

00:11:46.465 --> 00:11:48.985
who loves and cares about me.

00:11:50.505 --> 00:11:52.425
Unlike me,

00:11:52.945 --> 00:11:55.225
you're just a loser.

00:11:58.385 --> 00:12:01.305
You only landed your job

00:12:02.225 --> 00:12:04.065
thanks to your sugar mommy.

00:12:05.825 --> 00:12:08.305
And you're not even good at your job.

00:12:08.945 --> 00:12:10.865
All you do is kiss ass.

00:12:11.505 --> 00:12:12.905
Say it again.

00:12:16.105 --> 00:12:17.585
Do you want to know

00:12:18.625 --> 00:12:20.785
how people view you?

00:12:24.265 --> 00:12:26.825
You're holding our department back.

00:12:28.345 --> 00:12:30.225
You're so bad at your job.

00:12:30.865 --> 00:12:32.545
All bark and no bite.

00:12:34.185 --> 00:12:36.345
You kiss your boss's ass,

00:12:36.905 --> 00:12:39.545
and you're always stirring the pot.

00:12:40.505 --> 00:12:42.185
You better watch your mouth.

00:12:42.705 --> 00:12:44.625
Having a rich wife doesn't mean

00:12:44.705 --> 00:12:45.985
-you can say anything.
-So?

00:12:47.145 --> 00:12:49.105
So what if I have a rich wife?

00:12:49.185 --> 00:12:51.105
She's got nothing to do with this.

00:12:52.745 --> 00:12:54.825
What I'm saying is true, though.

00:12:55.465 --> 00:12:57.265
Your wife…

00:12:57.345 --> 00:12:59.785
Someone that rich
would never truly love anyone.

00:13:00.425 --> 00:13:02.865
Everyone knows she bought you for show--

00:13:03.905 --> 00:13:05.665
-Utt!
-Utt!

00:13:06.305 --> 00:13:09.825
If you say one more word
to disrespect Neen,

00:13:10.825 --> 00:13:13.985
I'll make sure you can't speak
for the rest of your life.

00:13:15.265 --> 00:13:16.905
-Stop it!
-Utt!

00:13:21.265 --> 00:13:23.425
If you lay a finger on Runch,

00:13:24.545 --> 00:13:26.585
I'll tell my uncle to fire you!

00:13:29.465 --> 00:13:30.625
Runch, let's go home.

00:13:45.905 --> 00:13:48.385
You're a lightweight,
no matter what you drink.

00:13:48.465 --> 00:13:49.865
Yet you still drank.

00:13:52.025 --> 00:13:53.625
I know, right?

00:13:54.225 --> 00:13:57.425
But he said

00:13:57.505 --> 00:14:01.185
you only ever let me drink expensive wine

00:14:02.465 --> 00:14:06.585
that's soft and soothing.

00:14:08.185 --> 00:14:11.145
That's why when I drink cheap booze,

00:14:11.225 --> 00:14:12.585
I get drunk so easily.

00:14:15.025 --> 00:14:18.665
It's just like that time
when I didn't want to eat fermented fish,

00:14:19.265 --> 00:14:21.745
and he said it was because

00:14:22.425 --> 00:14:24.945
I married someone rich

00:14:25.025 --> 00:14:28.465
and became such a snob
that I can't eat fermented fish.

00:14:28.545 --> 00:14:30.425
Come on, Runch.

00:14:30.505 --> 00:14:32.425
Please sit down.

00:14:32.945 --> 00:14:35.145
Everything!

00:14:35.225 --> 00:14:39.185
I don't get it.
This happens with everything.

00:14:39.265 --> 00:14:43.305
People blame everything on the fact

00:14:43.385 --> 00:14:45.825
that I married someone rich.
And then what?

00:14:45.905 --> 00:14:48.145
Then they say

00:14:48.225 --> 00:14:50.745
I married into money,

00:14:50.825 --> 00:14:54.425
when really I'm not
that kind of person at all.

00:14:55.345 --> 00:14:58.105
So us dating and getting married

00:14:58.185 --> 00:15:00.705
took away your pride, right?

00:15:00.785 --> 00:15:02.745
No.

00:15:03.465 --> 00:15:05.905
Then we should divorce
as soon as possible.

00:15:05.985 --> 00:15:08.745
That way, you'll get to live
a life you're proud of.

00:15:18.265 --> 00:15:19.385
Runch!

00:15:19.985 --> 00:15:22.185
I asked him

00:15:22.785 --> 00:15:25.305
if he's jealous of me

00:15:25.385 --> 00:15:27.425
because I have a beautiful,

00:15:27.505 --> 00:15:29.665
rich wife,

00:15:30.305 --> 00:15:32.505
who's also nice.

00:15:33.505 --> 00:15:36.545
It turned out he really is jealous of me

00:15:36.625 --> 00:15:38.745
for having a beautiful wife like you.

00:15:39.425 --> 00:15:41.625
I also found out

00:15:41.705 --> 00:15:45.345
that he slept with some old lady

00:15:46.505 --> 00:15:49.545
to land his job.

00:15:50.625 --> 00:15:52.865
And that's what you said to him earlier?

00:15:54.145 --> 00:15:55.305
Yeah.

00:15:55.385 --> 00:15:57.265
How did you learn all that?

00:15:58.505 --> 00:16:00.425
I saw them, of course.

00:16:01.465 --> 00:16:05.065
I saw them cuddling

00:16:05.145 --> 00:16:07.225
and making out.

00:16:11.705 --> 00:16:13.705
You drank a lot, didn't you?

00:16:13.785 --> 00:16:15.905
You never got this drunk before.

00:16:20.545 --> 00:16:21.825
Nope!

00:16:23.345 --> 00:16:25.505
I'm not drunk.

00:16:27.345 --> 00:16:29.025
Maybe a little.

00:16:29.985 --> 00:16:32.865
But I'm not so drunk
that I've lost control.

00:16:34.705 --> 00:16:36.545
It's just that

00:16:37.065 --> 00:16:40.225
I have less patience than usual.

00:16:42.985 --> 00:16:46.225
I was surprised, though. I was.

00:16:48.465 --> 00:16:49.465
It's good, though.

00:16:51.185 --> 00:16:52.505
Really?

00:16:53.705 --> 00:16:56.425
You want me to have no patience, Neen?

00:16:57.345 --> 00:16:59.425
Well, it's because you're very patient.

00:17:01.065 --> 00:17:02.905
That's why we ended up like this.

00:17:12.265 --> 00:17:15.184
But is it just me,

00:17:16.424 --> 00:17:20.424
or are you being nicer to me
than usual today?

00:17:26.184 --> 00:17:27.905
Neen.

00:17:29.425 --> 00:17:31.065
Then,

00:17:31.145 --> 00:17:34.665
can you be nice to me
just a little longer?

00:17:37.425 --> 00:17:38.745
What do you want?

00:17:42.545 --> 00:17:45.425
Can I sleep next to you?

00:17:45.505 --> 00:17:49.345
Please. Can we sleep together?

00:17:53.505 --> 00:17:55.305
Neen.

00:17:57.665 --> 00:18:01.265
Can I really sleep here tonight?

00:18:02.505 --> 00:18:06.385
Stop asking, or just go sleep
in your room. Go.

00:18:07.105 --> 00:18:11.025
Alright. I'll stop.

00:18:14.025 --> 00:18:16.865
I want to thank you, Neen.

00:18:16.945 --> 00:18:19.505
Thank you for picking me up

00:18:19.585 --> 00:18:21.905
and thank you

00:18:21.985 --> 00:18:24.945
for letting me sleep here.

00:18:25.025 --> 00:18:27.385
-Thank you so much.
-Sure.

00:18:27.465 --> 00:18:29.985
Are you done? I'm going to sleep.

00:18:37.705 --> 00:18:39.025
What?

00:18:41.505 --> 00:18:43.025
Neen.

00:18:43.785 --> 00:18:46.425
Did you really have
to put that pillow between us?

00:18:46.505 --> 00:18:48.105
Go to sleep.

00:18:58.145 --> 00:18:59.825
Give me a break.

00:19:33.825 --> 00:19:35.745
What are you doing?

00:19:37.425 --> 00:19:39.425
I'm cuddling you.

00:19:40.225 --> 00:19:44.385
I just want to cuddle you.
Nothing else.

00:19:45.105 --> 00:19:47.825
-Let go of me.
-Nope.

00:19:50.345 --> 00:19:51.785
Let go.

00:19:51.865 --> 00:19:53.185
Nope.

00:19:53.265 --> 00:19:54.825
You're not letting go, huh?

00:21:25.465 --> 00:21:27.145
You're just gonna drink coffee?

00:21:28.945 --> 00:21:30.505
That's all you're having too.

00:21:32.545 --> 00:21:34.425
I'm not very hungry.

00:21:37.265 --> 00:21:40.185
I was already full last night.

00:21:40.785 --> 00:21:41.825
Cheeky!

00:21:42.345 --> 00:21:44.065
What do you mean "cheeky"?

00:21:44.585 --> 00:21:46.785
I got full after I ate dinner.

00:21:47.905 --> 00:21:50.225
What did you think I meant?

00:21:53.185 --> 00:21:54.625
Go to work already.

00:21:57.185 --> 00:21:58.585
Wait.

00:22:01.705 --> 00:22:04.665
-Yes?
-Wanna have lunch together?

00:22:07.785 --> 00:22:10.865
We should only eat together
when necessary.

00:22:13.025 --> 00:22:14.985
So you're done being nice to me now?

00:22:17.465 --> 00:22:21.265
As long as we don't fight so much
it takes a toll on our mental health,

00:22:21.345 --> 00:22:22.665
that's good enough for me.

00:22:25.745 --> 00:22:28.825
-Got it.
-As for last night,

00:22:28.905 --> 00:22:32.665
we hadn't done
that kind of stuff in a while.

00:22:32.745 --> 00:22:35.425
It's only natural
our bodies were craving for it.

00:22:35.505 --> 00:22:38.385
Let's think of it as mutual fun.

00:22:50.065 --> 00:22:52.025
So that means,

00:22:52.105 --> 00:22:53.825
while we're waiting for our divorce,

00:22:54.505 --> 00:22:57.945
I can sleep with you all the time, right?

00:23:02.825 --> 00:23:06.665
This kind of thing
requires mutual consent.

00:23:07.825 --> 00:23:10.345
If you want it, but I don't,

00:23:10.985 --> 00:23:12.705
it's never gonna happen.

00:23:17.385 --> 00:23:20.145
Then, whenever you want it,

00:23:21.545 --> 00:23:24.065
you can call me anytime.

00:23:25.665 --> 00:23:27.785
Or you can be the one to initiate,

00:23:27.865 --> 00:23:30.105
like last night.

00:23:38.025 --> 00:23:40.305
See you at noon.

00:23:46.825 --> 00:23:49.065
If you hadn't stopped me,

00:23:49.145 --> 00:23:50.985
I would've punched her back.

00:23:51.065 --> 00:23:53.305
-I don't care if she's a woman.
-Come on, Utt.

00:23:54.065 --> 00:23:58.265
What? Does she think she can do
whatever she wants because she's our boss?

00:23:58.345 --> 00:23:59.905
She insulted me in front of everyone,

00:24:00.625 --> 00:24:01.865
treating me like trash.

00:24:01.945 --> 00:24:05.545
What? Does she think having connections
and a rich wife means

00:24:05.625 --> 00:24:07.385
she can act all high and mighty here?

00:24:07.465 --> 00:24:09.385
Quiet down, Utt. She'll hear you.

00:24:09.465 --> 00:24:12.225
Then let her! You know what,

00:24:12.305 --> 00:24:15.265
she's lucky I wasn't drunk enough.
Otherwise…

00:24:15.345 --> 00:24:16.785
Otherwise what?

00:24:25.585 --> 00:24:28.265
I heard everything you said.

00:24:32.705 --> 00:24:34.585
I'll say it just once.

00:24:35.585 --> 00:24:37.705
Don't talk behind my back.

00:24:38.465 --> 00:24:40.585
Say it to my face.

00:24:41.745 --> 00:24:43.745
Be a man.

00:24:45.945 --> 00:24:49.665
From now on,
if any of you is unhappy with me,

00:24:50.905 --> 00:24:52.305
please come talk to me.

00:24:54.585 --> 00:24:57.305
Don't gather and gossip

00:24:57.385 --> 00:24:59.065
as if this was some wet market.

00:25:05.065 --> 00:25:06.625
And also,

00:25:07.585 --> 00:25:11.425
if I catch any of you putting more effort
into gossiping than doing your job,

00:25:13.225 --> 00:25:15.985
I'll have to do some consideration.

00:25:17.145 --> 00:25:19.065
Since you all think

00:25:19.145 --> 00:25:21.905
I got to be the boss
because I pulled some strings

00:25:21.985 --> 00:25:23.305
and I had connections

00:25:24.705 --> 00:25:27.185
because my wife is the niece of the CEO,

00:25:28.945 --> 00:25:31.985
I'll use whatever you all think I have

00:25:32.065 --> 00:25:33.865
to the company's advantage.

00:25:35.065 --> 00:25:37.625
Now we'll know who really does their job

00:25:38.505 --> 00:25:40.745
and who's holding everyone back.

00:25:59.385 --> 00:26:00.865
EVERY RECEIPT CAN BE REDEEMED
AS M POINTS VIA THE M CARD APP

00:26:00.945 --> 00:26:02.425
THANK YOU! PLEASE COME AGAIN

00:26:21.105 --> 00:26:22.065
ASK SALES ASSOCIATES IF YOUR PURCHASE
CAN BE REDEEMED AS M POINTS

00:26:30.825 --> 00:26:32.265
That was a lot to sign.

00:27:08.825 --> 00:27:10.265
Come on in.

00:27:21.825 --> 00:27:23.825
Your food's here.

00:27:26.425 --> 00:27:29.505
How cunning. You brought my food here.

00:27:29.585 --> 00:27:30.625
Why?

00:27:31.145 --> 00:27:33.145
Were you afraid
I'd refuse to have lunch with you?

00:27:33.945 --> 00:27:35.345
Correct.

00:27:36.025 --> 00:27:38.025
You're basically twisting my arm.

00:27:44.785 --> 00:27:47.825
Here. Want me to feed you?

00:28:00.425 --> 00:28:04.305
If it makes people think
we love each other, please do it.

00:28:06.865 --> 00:28:10.065
There are many more things we can do

00:28:10.625 --> 00:28:13.345
to make it look like
we really love each other.

00:28:13.425 --> 00:28:15.945
Really? Then do it all.

00:28:16.545 --> 00:28:17.345
Are you sure?

00:28:22.585 --> 00:28:24.185
But don't do something crazy.

00:28:27.025 --> 00:28:28.665
-Is it inappropriate?
-Yeah.

00:28:31.265 --> 00:28:32.585
Then…

00:28:35.425 --> 00:28:36.985
Hey!

00:28:38.745 --> 00:28:40.265
That should do it.

00:28:49.665 --> 00:28:51.385
But right now,

00:28:52.305 --> 00:28:55.105
I really want to kiss you for real, Neen.

00:28:58.385 --> 00:29:00.425
We're in Thailand.

00:29:00.505 --> 00:29:04.265
Even though we're married,
I don't think kissing in public

00:29:04.345 --> 00:29:05.865
is a good idea.

00:29:07.305 --> 00:29:09.225
It's unlike if we were abroad, right?

00:29:10.185 --> 00:29:13.905
If we were abroad,
we could kiss anytime and anywhere.

00:29:14.785 --> 00:29:16.185
Yeah.

00:29:16.265 --> 00:29:19.065
Come on. Sit properly.

00:29:20.545 --> 00:29:22.345
Go.

00:29:35.905 --> 00:29:37.185
Yes, Mom?

00:29:40.585 --> 00:29:42.865
Sure. Okay.

00:29:44.945 --> 00:29:46.385
What's up?

00:29:48.345 --> 00:29:52.465
Dad's not home tonight,
so my mom wants me to sleep at her place.

00:29:53.065 --> 00:29:55.665
Are you just telling me,
or do you want me to sleep there too?

00:29:57.985 --> 00:30:00.825
If I invite you, will you come?

00:30:02.065 --> 00:30:05.425
Seeing your mom's face
makes it hard for me to eat or sleep.

00:30:05.505 --> 00:30:06.905
I thought so.

00:30:08.825 --> 00:30:09.865
But actually,

00:30:11.185 --> 00:30:13.145
if your mom doesn't see my face,

00:30:13.225 --> 00:30:16.745
she'll be eating and sleeping too well.

00:30:17.945 --> 00:30:21.225
I changed my mind. I'm going too.

00:30:21.305 --> 00:30:24.545
You mean you'll come with me?

00:30:24.625 --> 00:30:25.785
Yes.

00:30:27.265 --> 00:30:28.545
Why?

00:30:33.905 --> 00:30:36.345
Can't I come with you?

00:30:38.105 --> 00:30:40.745
It's been a couple of days
since she saw my face.

00:30:40.825 --> 00:30:42.865
She must miss her daughter-in-law so bad.

00:30:43.905 --> 00:30:46.145
If you two meet, you'll only fight.

00:30:46.225 --> 00:30:48.625
Isn't it better for you
to stay away from each other?

00:30:49.825 --> 00:30:52.785
Why? Are you afraid I'd bad-mouth
your mom so much it'd shock her?

00:30:53.385 --> 00:30:54.665
Neen!

00:30:55.905 --> 00:30:59.625
I'd do anything
to make that old hag unhappy.

00:31:05.785 --> 00:31:07.025
Thank you.

00:31:14.705 --> 00:31:16.385
What did you order?

00:31:18.025 --> 00:31:20.945
I don't get to stay at your mom's much,

00:31:21.025 --> 00:31:24.625
so I wanted to cook her something.

00:31:26.385 --> 00:31:28.305
What are you planning

00:31:28.385 --> 00:31:30.505
to cook for her, Neen?

00:31:31.905 --> 00:31:35.425
I won't tell you. It's a secret.
You'll know once we get to her place.

00:31:52.545 --> 00:31:54.985
Neen. I think

00:31:55.545 --> 00:31:57.665
you might want to wear a jacket.

00:31:57.745 --> 00:32:00.305
No. This is how I want to dress.

00:32:00.385 --> 00:32:02.105
You like women who show a lot of skin, no?

00:32:03.665 --> 00:32:06.145
I don't like women who show a lot of skin.

00:32:06.705 --> 00:32:09.065
I only like it when you do.

00:32:13.945 --> 00:32:15.465
Wait up, Neen!

00:32:26.585 --> 00:32:28.265
Hello, Mom.

00:32:29.825 --> 00:32:31.585
I thought Runch was coming alone.

00:32:32.305 --> 00:32:34.385
That was my plan too.

00:32:34.465 --> 00:32:36.505
But then Runch got upset.

00:32:36.585 --> 00:32:37.945
Why would she be upset?

00:32:38.025 --> 00:32:40.985
She stays the night here often,
and she's always been okay with it.

00:32:41.065 --> 00:32:43.705
She actually isn't okay
every time we aren't together.

00:32:43.785 --> 00:32:46.185
She just never told you.

00:32:46.265 --> 00:32:48.145
She only told me.

00:32:48.225 --> 00:32:52.505
And how could I say she's not okay
every time she's away from her wife?

00:32:52.585 --> 00:32:54.425
I didn't want to upset you.

00:32:55.865 --> 00:32:57.745
I wasn't expecting two guests,

00:32:57.825 --> 00:33:00.425
so I didn't prepare enough food.

00:33:00.505 --> 00:33:02.665
That won't be a problem, Mom.

00:33:02.745 --> 00:33:06.185
I'll be your chef today.

00:33:06.265 --> 00:33:09.185
I'm sure you'll be pleased.

00:33:19.145 --> 00:33:20.625
What's that?

00:33:38.985 --> 00:33:40.985
What exactly are you making?

00:33:41.665 --> 00:33:43.145
Can you tell me already?

00:33:44.705 --> 00:33:46.585
I told you I can't.

00:33:47.185 --> 00:33:48.385
Please go wait with your mom.

00:33:49.265 --> 00:33:52.625
Let me just say this meal will be exotic.

00:33:58.345 --> 00:34:00.385
Go wait with your mom. There.

00:34:17.145 --> 00:34:19.264
Your wife won't tell you
what she's making?

00:34:19.344 --> 00:34:20.465
No, Mom.

00:34:20.545 --> 00:34:22.425
She won't poison me, will she?

00:34:22.505 --> 00:34:25.185
Neen isn't that cruel, Mom.

00:34:25.264 --> 00:34:26.304
She could do way worse.

00:34:26.385 --> 00:34:29.225
Neen hates my guts.
You think I don't know that?

00:34:29.304 --> 00:34:31.985
But you hate her too, don't you?

00:34:37.385 --> 00:34:38.385
Neen!

00:34:40.505 --> 00:34:41.865
Honey!

00:34:47.425 --> 00:34:50.145
What happened here? Huh?

00:34:52.344 --> 00:34:54.505
Why are there so many frogs here?

00:34:54.585 --> 00:34:56.264
I was trying to make you

00:34:56.344 --> 00:34:58.825
spicy stir-fried frog.
But I dropped the box,

00:34:58.905 --> 00:35:01.025
so all the frogs got out!

00:35:01.105 --> 00:35:02.625
What do we do now?!

00:35:16.945 --> 00:35:17.945
Mom!

00:35:18.825 --> 00:35:21.665
Oh no! Mom!

00:35:23.825 --> 00:35:25.225
I got all of them.

00:35:25.305 --> 00:35:26.985
Thank you so much.

00:35:27.065 --> 00:35:29.625
-Please release them.
-Sure.

00:35:32.665 --> 00:35:35.505
Mom, I'm really sorry.

00:35:35.585 --> 00:35:38.145
Now you don't get to eat
spicy stir-fried frog.

00:35:38.225 --> 00:35:40.065
You were messing with me!

00:35:40.705 --> 00:35:44.305
I wasn't. I promise I meant well.
I really wanted you to eat it.

00:35:44.905 --> 00:35:47.385
Frogs are good for old people.

00:35:47.465 --> 00:35:49.265
They're high in protein, low in fat,

00:35:49.345 --> 00:35:52.905
and rich in minerals. They're good
for your brain and nervous system.

00:35:52.985 --> 00:35:55.345
They also keep your bones strong

00:35:55.425 --> 00:35:58.385
and boost your immune system
so you won't die so soon.

00:36:00.145 --> 00:36:03.385
How trashy and rude.
Didn't your parents teach you better?

00:36:03.465 --> 00:36:05.105
They did.

00:36:05.185 --> 00:36:08.505
They taught me to be respectful
to those who deserve it.

00:36:10.385 --> 00:36:11.905
And I don't think you do.

00:36:14.065 --> 00:36:14.945
Runch.

00:36:17.145 --> 00:36:20.465
Runch, you should have dinner
with your mom.

00:36:20.545 --> 00:36:22.305
I'll go to my room now.

00:36:23.105 --> 00:36:26.665
Once you're done,
please hurry and come on up.

00:36:26.745 --> 00:36:28.505
I'll serve you your dessert.

00:36:37.385 --> 00:36:38.945
Why didn't you help me tell her off?

00:36:39.665 --> 00:36:43.225
Mom. I don't know what to say anymore.

00:36:43.305 --> 00:36:45.145
And I'm tired of it.

00:36:45.865 --> 00:36:48.585
How come you only listen to her?
You won't listen to me!

00:36:50.825 --> 00:36:54.505
Mom, what do you want to have for dinner?

00:36:54.585 --> 00:36:56.545
I'll order it for you.

00:36:56.625 --> 00:36:59.105
No. I don't want to eat.

00:37:21.985 --> 00:37:23.425
Neen.

00:37:24.625 --> 00:37:27.145
If you're gonna lecture me, don't bother.

00:37:27.665 --> 00:37:28.785
I don't want to hear it.

00:37:35.265 --> 00:37:36.505
Please listen to me.

00:37:55.665 --> 00:37:57.625
What are you doing, Neen?

00:38:07.625 --> 00:38:09.385
-Runch… Runch…
-What are you doing, Neen?

00:38:09.465 --> 00:38:11.225
Runch, please don't do this.

00:38:12.785 --> 00:38:15.385
-Neen, stop.
-What do you mean, "stop"?

00:38:15.465 --> 00:38:18.105
-I don't want to stop yet.
-What are you doing?

00:38:18.185 --> 00:38:20.825
Making your mother go deaf
with my voice, of course.

00:38:20.905 --> 00:38:24.345
Your mom's always overthinking,
so I'll make her overthink even worse.

00:38:26.745 --> 00:38:28.185
Neen!

00:38:31.545 --> 00:38:33.865
Please stop. Mom will get us wrong.

00:38:36.385 --> 00:38:39.065
Runch, I told you to stop!

00:38:39.145 --> 00:38:40.545
-Enough, Neen.
-Open the door!

00:38:40.625 --> 00:38:42.945
What did you do to my daughter, Neen?!

00:38:43.025 --> 00:38:46.225
Open the door now! Open it!

00:38:46.305 --> 00:38:48.345
Stay out of this! I am--

00:38:48.425 --> 00:38:52.145
-Don't bite me, Runch. That hurt!
-I told you to open the door!

00:38:52.225 --> 00:38:53.545
Open it!

00:38:53.625 --> 00:38:56.065
-Neen.
-Why do you always bite me like that?

00:38:56.145 --> 00:38:59.265
It hurts, Runch.

00:39:01.425 --> 00:39:02.865
Cut it out!

00:39:40.265 --> 00:39:41.665
Was that fun?

00:39:49.345 --> 00:39:50.585
But now,

00:39:51.225 --> 00:39:53.585
you're asking for trouble.

00:39:54.265 --> 00:39:55.585
You know that, right?

00:40:18.065 --> 00:40:22.105
I told you to get along with her,
not get it on with her.

00:40:22.185 --> 00:40:23.945
Watch your mouth!

00:40:24.025 --> 00:40:26.065
Well, didn't you two,

00:40:26.145 --> 00:40:27.865
you know… last night?

00:40:27.945 --> 00:40:30.465
-You already know. Don't ask.
-Hey.

00:40:30.545 --> 00:40:33.065
And did the old loudmouth know

00:40:33.145 --> 00:40:36.385
what you and Runch were doing
in the next room?

00:40:39.865 --> 00:40:41.225
Of course she knew.

00:40:41.305 --> 00:40:44.505
I went all out and got super loud.
I bet she was up all night.

00:40:59.225 --> 00:41:02.145
I was gone for one night, and you
missed me so bad you couldn't sleep?

00:41:02.225 --> 00:41:03.785
As if!

00:41:03.865 --> 00:41:06.985
I couldn't sleep
because the devil was here.

00:41:07.065 --> 00:41:09.185
Devil? What devil?

00:41:09.265 --> 00:41:12.585
That brat, of course!
She was staying with Runch last night.

00:41:13.825 --> 00:41:15.745
And she… She…

00:41:17.865 --> 00:41:21.625
She did something totally inappropriate
in my house.

00:41:22.345 --> 00:41:24.305
And you saw it?

00:41:25.105 --> 00:41:27.705
I didn't. But I heard it.

00:41:28.865 --> 00:41:30.865
And all night too.

00:41:31.745 --> 00:41:34.025
She was like, "Runch, honey."

00:41:37.785 --> 00:41:38.905
I'm going to pass out.

00:41:40.145 --> 00:41:43.665
The most inappropriate thing
about last night

00:41:43.745 --> 00:41:45.105
was you!

00:41:45.785 --> 00:41:48.185
Why'd you stand there
and eavesdrop as they do it?

00:41:49.465 --> 00:41:52.105
Look, Pong. I wasn't eavesdropping.

00:41:52.185 --> 00:41:54.905
I was just worried about my daughter.

00:41:56.025 --> 00:41:58.065
Were you worried or curious?

00:41:58.145 --> 00:42:01.825
Curious? What would I
be curious about, Pong?

00:42:01.905 --> 00:42:04.465
I was just afraid
she used black magic on my daughter.

00:42:06.105 --> 00:42:08.905
I went on a dhamma retreat,
and my mind's been peaceful.

00:42:09.505 --> 00:42:12.665
And now that I'm back,
you made me realize one more thing.

00:42:12.745 --> 00:42:13.905
What?

00:42:15.305 --> 00:42:17.465
Our daughter has a life of her own.

00:42:18.065 --> 00:42:20.265
Her life isn't ours.

00:42:20.345 --> 00:42:23.065
We brought her into this world
and raised her.

00:42:23.785 --> 00:42:26.065
But we don't live her life.

00:42:27.145 --> 00:42:28.585
Whoever she loves,

00:42:29.305 --> 00:42:32.105
it's up to her heart to decide, not you.

00:42:33.145 --> 00:42:35.425
-But--
-I know you love Runch a lot.

00:42:38.265 --> 00:42:40.905
But you love her and force her,

00:42:41.625 --> 00:42:44.145
leaving her exhausted and uncomfortable.

00:42:44.665 --> 00:42:46.185
Eventually,

00:42:46.265 --> 00:42:48.825
she'll pull away from you.

00:42:51.265 --> 00:42:53.985
She's all grown now. She's an adult.

00:42:54.505 --> 00:42:56.505
She has the right to choose
what makes her happy.

00:42:57.345 --> 00:42:59.945
You don't get to choose it.

00:43:00.705 --> 00:43:03.305
You need to back off a little, Ging.

00:43:05.665 --> 00:43:07.225
There's no way I'm backing off.

00:43:07.785 --> 00:43:11.065
If I did, that'd mean
I've lost to that brat.

00:43:40.945 --> 00:43:41.945
Here's your blouse.

00:43:42.025 --> 00:43:44.825
It's already washed. Thanks again.

00:43:45.745 --> 00:43:47.185
You're welcome.

00:43:47.265 --> 00:43:50.185
Try not to spill coffee on yourself again.

00:43:51.705 --> 00:43:53.945
I'll be more careful.

00:43:58.185 --> 00:43:59.665
Ms. Neen.

00:44:03.825 --> 00:44:04.905
Yes?

00:44:12.945 --> 00:44:14.305
What is it, Ms. Runch?

00:44:15.625 --> 00:44:17.505
Are you free today?

00:44:19.545 --> 00:44:21.585
If you don't mind,

00:44:21.665 --> 00:44:24.225
I'd like to treat you to dinner.

00:44:28.825 --> 00:44:30.345
But if you're busy, I get it.

00:44:31.065 --> 00:44:33.185
Who said I was?

00:44:34.345 --> 00:44:36.625
And if you want to treat me,

00:44:36.705 --> 00:44:38.105
I'm down too.

00:44:42.305 --> 00:44:44.345
Now that we know each other,

00:44:44.425 --> 00:44:46.465
Why don't we drop the "Ms."?

00:44:47.505 --> 00:44:48.785
Runch.

00:44:49.985 --> 00:44:51.225
You're younger than me?

00:44:51.305 --> 00:44:52.665
Of course I am.

00:44:57.145 --> 00:44:58.385
Neen.

00:45:00.385 --> 00:45:01.545
Do you like that?

00:45:03.305 --> 00:45:05.025
That depends on who says it.

00:45:06.345 --> 00:45:09.865
If it's you, you can call me
whatever you like.

00:45:14.065 --> 00:45:16.385
There's one more thing I want to call you.

00:45:18.305 --> 00:45:19.865
What is it?

00:45:19.945 --> 00:45:21.945
"Gorgeous."

00:45:26.345 --> 00:45:28.665
You're really pretty.

00:45:31.265 --> 00:45:32.545
Thank you.

00:45:34.265 --> 00:45:35.265
I like.

00:45:38.025 --> 00:45:40.305
I mean, I like pretty girls.

00:45:46.185 --> 00:45:47.065
Sure.

00:45:48.385 --> 00:45:50.985
I'm glad to hear that.

00:45:59.465 --> 00:46:01.585
Morning, Gorgeous.

00:46:01.665 --> 00:46:04.145
Don't forget to drink
your favorite coffee today.

00:46:11.945 --> 00:46:13.585
Done, as ordered.

00:46:13.665 --> 00:46:16.585
RUNCH

00:46:19.905 --> 00:46:23.185
YOU HAVE 1 NEW MESSAGE

00:46:24.265 --> 00:46:26.945
Did you have lunch yet, Neen?

00:46:27.705 --> 00:46:30.825
Not yet. I want to savor
how much you miss me first.

00:46:40.465 --> 00:46:41.905
Good night, Runch.

00:46:45.145 --> 00:46:46.705
Good night, Neen.

00:47:06.265 --> 00:47:08.505
It's nice to see you again.

00:47:08.585 --> 00:47:09.505
Here you go.

00:47:11.745 --> 00:47:14.145
Aren't you going to read that text?

00:47:14.225 --> 00:47:15.145
No.

00:47:15.225 --> 00:47:17.825
Because I'm having dinner
with you right now.

00:47:17.905 --> 00:47:19.265
Let's hold hands and head inside.

00:47:19.905 --> 00:47:22.025
You're obviously feeling jealous.

00:47:22.105 --> 00:47:24.465
Why would I get jealous?
We're getting divorced anyway.

00:47:24.545 --> 00:47:26.225
You like Runch, right?

00:47:26.305 --> 00:47:27.585
Aunt Ging!

00:47:30.465 --> 00:47:32.305
Let's just keep hugging.
It warms my heart.

00:48:14.825 --> 00:48:17.305
Subtitle translation by:
Ramil Natnitiwitaya